{"tid":1103388,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"唔剃汗毛好影響儀容, 一定要剃!!","createTime":"2019-04-12T11:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T13:13:08.000Z","uid":209157,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"833e6371887faa7761a0eb69288cc25fb8efdcf0","tid":1103388,"uid":209157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"講清楚先, 係嘴邊嘅汗毛, 男人一定要剃!<br />\n<br />\n而家間中見到啲90後末/00後男仔唇邊有濃密嘅汗毛唔剃, 如果你係其中一個, 咁我呼籲你馬上剃咗佢 注意下儀容啦 睇落整潔好多架!<br />\n<br />\n根據我個人經歷 我整理咗3個最常聽到唔剃汗毛嘅理由 <br />\n<br />\n1. &quot;剃咗會睇落好bb好小學雞㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;<br />\n呢個諗法通常出現於啱啱升上高中冇耐 開始生得多毛 咁佢地就會覺得 &quot;ahh我生鬚啦似翻個大人啦&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你可能對剃毛剃鬚有誤解 汗毛就人人都有 但係男人留鬚係可以型嘅 而汗毛唔剃就俾人感覺好核突好污糟嘅 好像昆蟲條觸鬚咁 何況汗毛同鬚本來就唔同 唔好以為嘴唇上多咗兩條紫菜就覺得係鬍啦 唔型架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有機會翻母校 見到中四嘅課室入面個個男仔啲汗毛都長到仆街 我諗翻其實以前我都係咁 而家睇翻相都覺核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以其實呢個思想本來就係bb嘅表現 唔好呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. &quot;如果剃咗啲毛 鬍根會越嚟越硬架&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個理由就同&quot;飲水個人會急尿架&quot;本質上一樣啦 冇錯鬍根係會硬嘅 但都唔係唔剃嘅理由 我真係諗唔到有乜論點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贏哂 我只能講你個樣係用嚟見人嘅 你有都唔剃咁污糟行出街見人你介唔介意俾人覺得你毒撚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁如果你要見工,翻intern, 揾份m記parttime 我唔信你會唔執下個樣就去 咁點解嗰啲時候就要做靚仔 但平時又唔剃汗毛俾人感覺整潔啲?<br />\n<br />\n3. 懶 / 覺得no one cares<br />\n呢個理由冇得頂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我以前唔肯剃鬚嘅時候俾老母話似塘虱, 有次要影証件相時老母叫我唔好好似條塘虱咁影, 我唔知乜叫塘虱, 所以就問google大神, 以下呢條魚就係塘虱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tpn2p48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftpn2p48.jpg&h=7e50e547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我就知點解屋企人成日叫我剃汗毛啦 似毒撚, 唔乾淨, 非常影響儀容<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好多人都好積極剃嘅 但如果你唔係嘅 咁你讀完呢個po就唔好再揾藉口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為你好咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62400bbbef53089b88026e0d1bb955f0f2c9b806","tid":1103388,"uid":209157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"有冇經歷過唔願剃鬚嘅階段?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2246efec8ad9fe0ddbea7914d3544e80e8a8f7","tid":1103388,"uid":181971,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"好多女人都唔剃汗毛，更何況男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27874eedd881d3d02ba2af4ba34a7b8c5e3ffbdb","tid":1103388,"uid":190962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"唔剃幾靚仔都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289c2303d9c4c24a79727cccf13326aebac25cf7","tid":1103388,"uid":19005,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"咪撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到自己有剃"},{"pid":"5fd97cd24ad4bfead09147867e5faf1dcfdf22b4","tid":1103388,"uid":18196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"289c2303d9c4c24a79727cccf13326aebac25cf7","tid":1103388,"uid":19005,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"咪撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到自己有剃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11d26af389245d2166eafee30051c354785342f","tid":1103388,"uid":209157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12